\description{
Operating surplus or deficit as a share of total revenue, before depreciation.

\strong{Formula:}

\if{html}{\out{<div class="sourceCode">}}\preformatted{predpm = ( total_revenue - ( total_expenses - depreciation ) ) / total_revenue
